22
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,583
Leah... Baik.

23
00:03:26,166 --> 00:03:27,333
William...

24
00:03:38,416 --> 00:03:39,250
Baik.

25
00:03:53,583 --> 00:03:55,750
Teruslah... Baik.

26
00:04:28,791 --> 00:04:29,458
I--

27
00:04:29,958 --> 00:04:31,958
Ini hadiah yang aku mau.

28
